query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `domain_health_logs` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `domainId` int NOT NULL,
  `checkType` enum('dns','ssl','http') NOT NULL,
  `status` enum('success','warning','error') NOT NULL,
  `responseTime` int,
  `details` text,
  `errorMessage` text,
  `checkedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `domain_health_logs_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
